Donald Trump Signs "Right To Try" Act. <span>(Getty/Alex Wong)</span> </strong>
<h1>Order to print Trump's name on every stimulus check expected to delay payments to Americans</h1>
<h2>The president’s name will appear on the memo line of every payment, because he cannot legally sign the checks</h2>
</section>

<br />
